<i>noun</i>: 호들갑 [호들갑], 야단 [야ː단], 법석 [법썩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호들갑 [호들갑]</dt><br>
<dd>fuss; uproar; making a big deal; overreaction</dd><br>
<dd>가볍고 조심성이 없으며 야단스러운 말이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of acting or speaking in an imprudent, careless, and boisterous manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>야단 [야ː단]</dt><br>
<dd>1. uproar; tumult; clamor</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일 때문에 시끄럽게 자꾸 떠들거나 소란을 일으킴.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making a noise or making a row due to something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. scolding; chiding; rebuke</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 잘못을 큰소리로 혼냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of criticizing someone's mistake in a loud voice.</dd><br>
<dd>3. trouble; predicament; quandary</dd><br>
<dd>매우 곤란한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A very awkward situation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석 [법썩]</dt><br>
<dd>noise; fuss; uproar</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 떠드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A very loud scene.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>